{"tid":2052008,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聖保祿醫院貼告示不接受訪客佩戴 CuMask 入內 醫院範圍需佩戴外科口罩","createTime":"2020-06-05T07:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T10:47:12.000Z","uid":36494,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c67b2577581807f42ebed3553f37e51760553801","tid":2052008,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:53:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2662428#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2662428%23%26gid%3D1%26pid%3D1&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGRmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=a2ded8d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2662428#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=1</a>"},{"pid":"19cb31182fdb1a7d17d3de0d22845afb6bad8995","tid":2052008,"uid":36494,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SM6i8sE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSM6i8sE.png&h=8a126959&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acd40b6c5290db705e7e1a3e5049ceb9a8e56e0a","tid":2052008,"uid":36494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:54:50.000Z","msg":"特區政府在 5 月初，向全港市民每人發放一個可重用的「 CuMask 銅芯抗疫口罩」，以減輕市民在採購口罩上的壓力。不過，近日有私家醫院卻張貼告示，指醫院範圍內必須佩戴外科口罩，更以圖示表明其他種類口罩恕不接受，當中包括政府派發人人有份的 CuMask。<br />\n<br />\n港府在 5 月初向全港市民派發可重用的 CuMask<br />\n聖保祿醫院張貼告示指不接受訪客佩戴 CuMask 入內<br />\n表明醫院範圍內必須佩戴外科口罩<br />\n【相關報導】【CuMask 佩戴】何栢良建議 4 類人士避免使用銅芯抗疫口罩<br />\n<br />\n有網民在 Facebook 群組內發文並附上圖片，指聖保錄醫院內張貼告示指，醫院範圍內必須配戴外科口罩，其他種類（口罩）恕不接受，更以圖片舉例哪些口罩不合符外科口罩的要求，當中包括了政府派發的可重用 CuMask、氣閥口罩、布口罩及防毒面罩。而該名網民則指：「已 FC (Fact Checked)，正苦呀婆底褲係無 X 用」，意指政府派發的口罩對防禦病毒方面起不了太大作用。<br />\n<br />\n帖文隨即引來大量網民轉發關注，而 <a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGRmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=7752405a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 記者亦致電聖保祿醫院就有關事宜作查詢，不過在截稿前，醫院方面仍未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良早前曾建議，出現發燒、呼吸道感染病徵者、接受家居檢疫者、確診或懷疑個案者及其緊密接觸者，以及到醫院及老人院等高危地方人士，應避免使用 CuMask，以防口罩表面帶有病毒，在清洗期間增加傳播風險。"},{"pid":"63b0d20004167f41abafcec373e1bca78ecfd9c7","tid":2052008,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:56:35.000Z","msg":"講到明唔適合醫院用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15652b40b92c481cd5dd03dcc1c7a0625b404bf8","tid":2052008,"uid":335434,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/000301_8cfc5d53ec5ba932c73822d24f9623a5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F000301_8cfc5d53ec5ba932c73822d24f9623a5.png&h=1fc2da40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正常啊 你咁嘅款行入去 有邊間醫院會俾你入去啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64d7b113552461ed092bb8124c4bb560cba17f1","tid":2052008,"uid":173179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:57:47.000Z","msg":"賤撚過condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda3a88321426721549386b7de8969b6c835526b","tid":2052008,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:57:56.000Z","msg":"去醫院戴會變Killumask"},{"pid":"5584394fe2dea870ff25c555f335716e8afafa8d","tid":2052008,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15652b40b92c481cd5dd03dcc1c7a0625b404bf8","tid":2052008,"uid":335434,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/000301_8cfc5d53ec5ba932c73822d24f9623a5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F000301_8cfc5d53ec5ba932c73822d24f9623a5.png&h=1fc2da40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正常啊 你咁嘅款行入去 